@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rmdoat(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.83) / wp.abs(v0 + 0.78)) * v1)
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.cos(v0 + 0.83) / wp.exp(tmp + 0.48)))
    v2 = wp.sin((v0 + 0.30))
    v2 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.98 / v0 + 0.34)) / tmp)
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.exp(v0 + 0.46)))
    v2 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
